            "text": "Attacker may impersonate a legitimate physician by replaying or forging clinical query credentials, gaining unauthorized access to clinical recommendation views and patient data.",
            "markdown": "Implement mutual TLS authentication and short-lived signed JWT tokens with physician identity binding. Enforce step-up authentication for high-sensitivity clinical queries."
          },
